00Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77fc82a747d5e804cb7575e35d0534220da4a996","tid":1723533,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:11:56.000Z","msg":"<strong>他們在打的是「中共政權保衛戰」，而你們僅僅是在打「香港生活方式保衛戰」</strong><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（一） Be Water(水聚散) 不能變為Be Castle（碉堡戰、陣地戰）</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">對付Be Water，<strong>第一就是分化</strong>，<strong>把勇武派、和理非派拆分</strong>，<strong>第二步是下餌，引誘勇武派進入「必守的陣地」</strong>，刺激他們建立碉堡，最好所有的勇武派都集中進入少數陣地（例如四所大學），然後<strong>隔絕、撒網、一舉成擒</strong>。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（二） 從「誰才是暴徒」辯論陷阱脫身</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">港人對抗港府還算旗鼓相當，畢竟兩邊都是被法治洗禮過的香港人，<strong>但是港人對付中共的無底綫宣傳統戰技能</strong>，坦白說，<strong>還是太嫩</strong>。世人關心香港事態的焦點從「港人要自由、要自治」，變成「人民和政府誰才是暴力方」的辯論，這正是<strong>北京</strong>要製造的<strong>焦點轉移</strong>。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（三） 一切回歸三個字 &ndash; 真普選</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">核心訴求只有一個：真普選，一切口號、行動、宣傳，都環繞真普選這單一訴求展開，<strong>這樣，世界聽得懂，連中國內地人民都聽得懂</strong>。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"8aac3053a756031202ae0a52234e66447b42fe7e","tid":1723533,"uid":25100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T06:09:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad92704b9b053380ba5e372d34617f7d015c494","tid":1723533,"uid":25100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3afb00ecb06c773df7ad47b9c8041b8187d8ca35","tid":1723533,"uid":173016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:26:56.000Z","msg":"唔可以比班港豬過聖誕新年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1738306/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1738306/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"2bd8726f80f810e29fd65990ff5a23bca267de10","tid":1723533,"uid":166616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c05f34827fcada6b324e03e19e2cbead2ab094f5","tid":1723533,"uid":25100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:19:39.000Z","msg":"唔好早收或者被罷工之後週圍去飲飲食食<br />\n減少非黃店以外既不必要消費<br />\n我地既目標係隊淋個經濟<br />\n等商家比壓力政府同轉黃支持我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:27:24.000Z","msg":"堅持緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a02ad1e52ff40148c24796d8d24601d50af0e21a","tid":1723533,"uid":173016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:32:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1738306/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1738306/page/1</a><br />\n咁多手足被拉，被打，被女女女，被自殺，dllm班港豬仲可以咁開心？？<br />\n你老母食屎啦，香港無人可以置身其外<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我要聖誕新年個幾日日日開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"572ed625e8f1c696cf0fe3e87b2c4a95531bede6","tid":1723533,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:34:49.000Z","msg":"呢排真係慳左好多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3faedb73e011a13b2f4d910a58f3f71d6ef4e411","tid":1723533,"uid":47593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:42:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0aae3aed4cb2c738a84c3993118c18fef174285a","tid":1723533,"uid":47593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T08:42:32.